job.title: HP TET Teachers Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for Eligibility Test
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Available soon

Name of the post:

  • Test (TGT (Arts/ Medical/ Non Medical)/ Shastri/ L.T/ JBT/ Punjabi/ Urdu)

Description:

HP Board of School Education  issued a total of Various vacancies for the posts of Test (TGT (Arts/ Medical/ Non Medical)/ Shastri/ L.T/ JBT/ Punjabi/ Urdu) . The online application for these posts under HP TET shall start from 24-05-2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 13-06-2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for HP TET Teachers Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • The application fee for General & their Sub categories: Rs.800/-
  • The application fee for OBC/ ST/ SC/ PHH: Rs. 500/- 
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 24-05-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 13-06-2021 

Educational qualification:

  • You must have the degree in Graduation to apply for the post of Test (TGT (Arts/ Medical/ Non Medical)/ Shastri/ L.T/ JBT/ Punjabi/ Urdu) 

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is: 21 years
  • The maximum age required to apply is: 47 years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Test (TGT (Arts/ Medical/ Non Medical)/ is as per norms
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that HP TET issued this notification for which posts.

How to apply for HP TET Teachers Recruitment 2021 ?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of HP TET
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Test (TGT (Arts/ Medical/ Non Medical)/ Shastri/ L.T/ JBT/ Punjabi/ Urdu) 
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
